document_data.name: Nousoorn Street
document_data.mainbody: '''Nousoorn Street''' was a road found within the city of [[Suldolphor]] in far eastern [[Calimshan]].{{Cite interactive atlas|Suldolphor}}
document_data.Location: Nousoorn Street ran through the central section of Suldolphor near the harbor.
document_data.Notable Locations: An underground temple to [[Beshaba]] called the [[Deep House of Doom]] was located beneath Nousoorn Street.
